{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"iddd367429-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06","identifier":"/us/usc/t12/s4638"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4638"},"text":"§ 4638.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Private rights of action","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter shall not create any private right of action on behalf of any person against a regulated entity, or any director or executive officer of a regulated entity, or impair any existing private right of action under other applicable law.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"iddd36742a-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/550/tXIII/s1379A"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–550, title XIII, § 1379A","children":[],"tail":", formerly § 1378, "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3993"},"text":"106 Stat. 3993","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered § 1379A and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/289/dA/tI"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–289, div. A, title I","children":[],"tail":", §§ 1153(a)(1), 1156(b)(2), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2008-07-30"},"text":"July 30, 2008","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/122/2770"},"text":"122 Stat. 2770","children":[],"tail":", 2777.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"iddd36742b-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"iddd36742c-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"iddd36742d-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"This chapter, referred to in text, was in the original “this title and the amendments made by this title”, meaning title XIII of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/550"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–550","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1992-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 1992","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/106/3941"},"text":"106 Stat. 3941","children":[],"tail":", which is classified principally to this chapter. For complete classification of title XIII to the Code, see Short Title note set out under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s4501"},"text":"section 4501 of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"iddd36742e-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/550/s1379A"},"text":"section 1379A of Pub. L. 102–550","children":[],"tail":" was renumbered section 1379C and is classified to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s4640"},"text":"section 4640 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"iddd36742f-3a6f-11f1-8fa0-c065796a7f06"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2008—","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/110/289/s1156/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 110–289, § 1156(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “a regulated entity” for “an enterprise”, was executed by making the substitution in two places to reflect the probable intent of Congress."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
